#: vt_introduction.xml:208
#, no-c-format
msgid "Operating systems currently modified to run in paravirtual mode are called <emphasis>paravirtualized operating systems</emphasis> and include &productname; and NetWareÂ® 6.5 SP8."
msgstr ""

